title: WESTWORLD Season 3 Episode 1 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: I'm hoping to do breakdowns for every episode this season so make sure to subscribe to know as soon my videos come out. Love to hear your theories below!
I'm looking forward to being completely confused all season.
Out of all the breakdowns I’ve watched someone finally addressed Dolores’s dress change. Thank u
As if the storyline wasn’t complicated enough, now we gotta keep up with body swapping like Altered Carbon lol
The parallel between shots of Caleb waking up multiple times just as Dolores did in S1 was a fine detail. Makes me wonder if Caleb is a host with backstory.
description:
In this video we breakdown, explain, review, and recap Season 3 Episode 1 of HBO's Westworld for new theories and details you missed. The new season stars Aaron Paul, Evan Rachel Wood, Ed Harris and Jeffrey Wright.
